{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "648b5a63417cc3fb48d659fa", "type": "singleCorrect", "level": 3, "category": null, "approximateTimeRequired": 180, "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "source": "MOG", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d76b2c52ffa3c944600df"], "subjects": ["615d708dbd4a37c4058ee5a8"], "chapters": ["615d6fed2b295b085ab6eba2"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "microConcepts": [], "questionLabels": [], "previousYearPapers": [{"_id": "615d92eade3d91842a5cf7ce", "title": "JEE Main 2012 (12 May Online)", "isVisible": true}], "question": {"text": "We wish to make a microscope with the help of two positive lenses both with a focal length of 20 $\\mathrm{mm}$ each and the object is positioned $25 \\mathrm{~mm}$ from the objective lens. How far apart the lenses should be so that the final image is formed at infinity?", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "qfSzM", "text": "\n$20 \\mathrm{~mm}$\n", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "BcRR7", "text": "\n$100 \\mathrm{~mm}$\n", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "V70dC", "text": "\n$120 \\mathrm{~mm}$\n", "image": null, "isCorrect": true}, {"id": "a8j61", "text": "\n$80 \\mathrm{~mm}$", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "<img src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq/jee_main/HQ6I77Z0kD6IeFqgoOgG42mM0w1kX6tDGQtcnHid0zI.original.fullsize.png\"><br>\nTo obtain final image at infinity, object which is the image formed by objective should be at focal distance of eye-piece. By lens formula (for objective)\n$$\n\\begin{aligned}\n& \\frac{1}{v_0}-\\frac{1}{u_0}=\\frac{1}{f_0} \\\\\n\\text { or, } \\quad & \\frac{1}{v_0}-\\frac{1}{-25}=\\frac{1}{20} \\\\\n\\Rightarrow \\quad & \\frac{1}{v_0}=\\frac{1}{20}-\\frac{1}{25}=\\frac{5-4}{100}=\\frac{1}{100} \\mathrm{~mm} \\\\\n\\therefore \\quad & v_0=100 \\mathrm{~mm}\n\\end{aligned}\n$$\nTherefore the distance between the lenses\n$$\n=v_0+f_e=100 \\mathrm{~mm}+20 \\mathrm{~mm}=120 \\mathrm{~mm}\n$$", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "masterId": "MOGJMPYQ99114650", "numericalLowerLimit": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "bucket": "", "isRemoved": false, "cpyqbSubjects": ["61bb58181213731910ea0b70", "61c055eae8ce0dc8a5c62d33", "616057750283de43c87e3e1b", "61964fe0a5a5260118868021", "61964f81a5a526011886801d", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625b", "616057920283de43c87e3e1e", "615f0c729476412f48314dab", "61a8a2c2e8ce0dc8a5c62d2d", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352b", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7d", "616056cd0283de43c87e3e15", "616057190283de43c87e3e18", "62962075e7f8e9ac4daeafd7", "64d50bd73df7f4a7f3017f6f", "66b79b34d4b564dfab4f94cc", "678ea9a09cc79e5f592bdc11", "67fa5fef4468eb1307ceb0ad", "6807d2ad647479b8e8696479"], "cpyqbChapters": ["61964c922db938c3ec5c87e8", "6160243a86b518ff2afd9379", "6160243ae896b71d7f0f03d9", "61bb820fc1f688a120dfda9f", "61964c9102fe1de035852896", "61e7bd71a2dd607688d6c01b", "61c08989e3eba41a9e71354b", "61602437a04b762ba7dfcb47", "61602438690b07c861db4cc9", "6160243b7384a30f11cacc9e", "629109ef0299d67104ca49d5", "629f3a9295d059d5cc4d982e", "629621243e04d5d8ca7b92bd", "629f390e4eb9140dc965900d", "64eb06dd3118f713ecfef1b0", "66d5853ba75f05ee8564f575", "67921d651d5b5072da5e9aae", "67fdff46378e1624ea7b6984", "680920293a10446a207fdecb"], "cpyqbExams": ["615f0e999476412f48314daf", "616059af0283de43c87e3e23"]}}